rComments: most of students take this class towards breadth. if you take cr for this course, then it's quite easy to pass. Prof like to ask details (ex. percentage, tree species) on tests which is hard to memorize. Also, heavy work on memorizing all slides and extra required readings if you want to get high mark.

His slides are pretty uninformative, too many readings, and he mumbles so you can barely hear him in class. If someone coughs or makes any sort of noise you wont be able to hear him. I think he treats his lectures like a talk hed give instead of presenting the information in a constructive way
